2007-5-24   fabian

    * Fixed a timer bug in PTYSession introduced in the last change.
	
2007-5-23   fabian

    * Added a PASUE_MODE in PTYSession. Now the background sessions' timer stops when there's no activity. CPU usage reducde.
    
