2003-03-31	ujwal

    * Made URL parsing in PTYTextView slightly more 
      intelligent.

2003-03-30	ujwal

    * When dragging a text clipping onto iTerm, we 
      don't insert the file name of the clipping since 
      the contents are inserted.

